{"tid":126750,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"自 信 法 拉 挺 胸 感 性 背 心 雙 手 托 大 米","createTime":"2017-02-19T14:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T00:59:52.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1252,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1779eaf58237709138788f639d3490060e9a4800","tid":126750,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"法拉結束室內賽生涯<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170219/large/1487507628_c047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170219%2Flarge%2F1487507628_c047.jpg&h=1847a5a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際田聯世界室內巡迴賽最後一站比賽，上星期六喺英國伯明翰圓滿結束，英國中長跑好手法拉嘅室內賽生涯亦有一個完美句號，因為佢喺男子5,000米以13分09秒16獲得冠軍，將自己所保持嘅室內歐洲紀錄提高咗1秒多，而賽後33歲嘅法拉仲話呢次係佢最後一次參加室內賽，喺8月嘅世錦賽之後，就會正式轉戰公路賽。喺嚿年里約奧運完成男子5,000米及10,000米「兩金兩連霸」壯舉嘅法拉賽後話：「好難相信呢場係我最後一場室內賽，不過可以打破紀錄就更加意義重大！」"},{"pid":"583e9e7b647b5359f1e14be17e08349198a780ad","tid":126750,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5514707963329eb39ca803c25cd7ec988b16ca","tid":126750,"uid":28287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"好靚仔"},{"pid":"1d8f33c24d5017aec22aff90dcabcf38a5fbee20","tid":126750,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"Ok you win <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79918cac8f2f825e0285492d60e01cdd035398a1","tid":126750,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf0bba0089dc03dbd2f2f2dd28a020d5c87eb1f","tid":126750,"uid":1139,"like":0,